<<How do they work on our air-cooled vehicles? I read the .pdf file on
the water-cooled emissions results, and it makes mention of the fact
that it installs in a water hose.>> 

Eron, 

Real simple.

Remove 4 of the lower sump plate screws and using them, hang the engine
heater.

This project will take all of 5-10 minutes.

It heats the engine oil from the sump plate.

